{"comments":"Opacity - alpha transparency value.\n\nMeasured as a percentage from 0 to 100:\n- **0%**: Fully transparent (invisible)\n- **50%**: Half transparent\n- **100%**: Fully opaque (solid)\n\nUsed in RGBA, HSLA, and other color spaces with alpha channels.\nAlso known as alpha or transparency.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[67,40],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[67,1]},"title":"eqOpacity"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[68,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[68,1]},"title":"ordOpacity"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[71,35],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[70,1]},"title":"showOpacity"}],"comments":"Opacity value as percentage (0-100)\n\nRepresents alpha transparency. 0% is fully transparent, 100% is fully opaque.\nThis matches the pattern of other percentage-based atoms like Saturation and\nLightness for consistency across the Schema.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[65,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[65,1]},"title":"Opacity"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create an opacity value, clamping to 0-100\n\nValues outside the valid range are clamped:\n```purescript\nopacity 50   -- Opacity 50%\nopacity 150  -- Opacity 100% (clamped)\nopacity (-20) -- Opacity 0% (clamped)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[85,26],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[85,1]},"title":"opacity"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create an opacity value without clamping\n\nUse only when you know the value is valid (0-100).\nInvalid values will break invariants.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[92,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[92,1]},"title":"unsafeOpacity"},{"children":[],"comments":"Extract the raw Int value (0-100)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[230,25],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[230,1]},"title":"unwrap"},{"children":[],"comments":"Scale opacity by a factor (0.0 to 2.0 typical)\n\nUseful for fading effects:\n```purescript\nscale 0.5 (opacity 80)  -- Opacity 40%\nscale 2.0 (opacity 30)  -- Opacity 60%\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[130,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[130,1]},"title":"scale"},{"children":[],"comments":"Increase opacity by percentage points\n\nMakes something more opaque:\n```purescript\nincrease 20 (opacity 30)  -- Opacity 50%\nincrease 50 (opacity 80)  -- Opacity 100% (clamped)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[141,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[141,1]},"title":"increase"},{"children":[],"comments":"Decrease opacity by percentage points\n\nMakes something more transparent:\n```purescript\ndecrease 20 (opacity 50)  -- Opacity 30%\ndecrease 50 (opacity 30)  -- Opacity 0% (clamped)\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[151,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[151,1]},"title":"decrease"},{"children":[],"comments":"Invert opacity (100 - value)\n\nConverts transparency to opacity and vice versa:\n```purescript\ninvert (opacity 30)   -- Opacity 70%\ninvert (opacity 100)  -- Opacity 0%\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[161,29],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[161,1]},"title":"invert"},{"children":[],"comments":"Multiply two opacity values\n\nModels layering of transparent surfaces. Result is always more transparent\nthan either input (unless one is fully opaque):\n```purescript\nmultiply (opacity 50) (opacity 50)  -- Opacity 25%\nmultiply (opacity 80) (opacity 90)  -- Opacity 72%\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[172,42],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[172,1]},"title":"multiply"},{"children":[],"comments":"Blend two opacity values with weight (0.0 = all first, 1.0 = all second)\n\nLinear interpolation between two alpha values:\n```purescript\nblend 0.0 (opacity 20) (opacity 80)  -- Opacity 20%\nblend 0.5 (opacity 20) (opacity 80)  -- Opacity 50%\nblend 1.0 (opacity 20) (opacity 80)  -- Opacity 80%\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[184,49],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[184,1]},"title":"blend"},{"children":[],"comments":"Check if fully transparent (opacity = 0%)\n\nUseful for optimization - fully transparent layers don't need rendering:\n```purescript\nisTransparent (opacity 0)  -- true\nisTransparent (opacity 1)  -- false\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[201,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[201,1]},"title":"isTransparent"},{"children":[],"comments":"Check if fully opaque (opacity = 100%)\n\nUseful for optimization - fully opaque layers can occlude layers behind:\n```purescript\nisOpaque (opacity 100)  -- true\nisOpaque (opacity 99)   -- false\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[211,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[211,1]},"title":"isOpaque"},{"children":[],"comments":"Check if semi-transparent (0% < opacity < 100%)\n\nDetects cases requiring alpha blending:\n```purescript\nisSemiTransparent (opacity 50)   -- true\nisSemiTransparent (opacity 0)    -- false\nisSemiTransparent (opacity 100)  -- false\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Boolean"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[222,40],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[222,1]},"title":"isSemiTransparent"},{"children":[],"comments":"Bounds documentation for this type\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Bounded"],"IntBounds"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[264,28],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[264,1]},"title":"bounds"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert to Number for calculations\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[234,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[234,1]},"title":"toNumber"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert to unit interval (0.0-1.0)\n\nUseful for exporting to graphics APIs (CSS, WebGL, Canvas):\n```purescript\ntoUnitInterval (opacity 0)    -- 0.0\ntoUnitInterval (opacity 50)   -- 0.5\ntoUnitInterval (opacity 100)  -- 1.0\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[245,36],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[245,1]},"title":"toUnitInterval"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create opacity from unit interval (0.0-1.0)\n\nUseful for converting from graphics APIs that use normalized floats.\n```purescript\nfromUnitInterval 0.0  -- Opacity 0%\nfromUnitInterval 0.5  -- Opacity 50%\nfromUnitInterval 1.0  -- Opacity 100%\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[103,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[103,1]},"title":"fromUnitInterval"},{"children":[],"comments":"Convert to 8-bit channel value (0-255)\n\nUseful for serializing to RGBA8 formats:\n```purescript\ntoChannel (opacity 0)    -- 0\ntoChannel (opacity 50)   -- 128\ntoChannel (opacity 100)  -- 255\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[256,28],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[256,1]},"title":"toChannel"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create opacity from 8-bit channel value (0-255)\n\nUseful for converting RGBA8 formats where alpha is stored as a byte.\n```purescript\nfromChannel 0    -- Opacity 0%\nfromChannel 128  -- Opacity 50%\nfromChannel 255  -- Opacity 100%\n```\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Opacity"],"Opacity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[114,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Opacity.purs","start":[114,1]},"title":"fromChannel"}],"name":"Hydrogen.Schema.Color.Opacity","reExports":[]}